A tab system based on Scriptaculous and Prototype.js.

[![Code Climate](https://codeclimate.com/repos/52f68088e30ba0365a015072/badges/183235c0f7e4f4f0a857/gpa.png)](https://codeclimate.com/repos/52f68088e30ba0365a015072/feed)

Goals:

* Easy tab panel creation from basic markup
* Easy dynamic addition of tabs
* Drag & drop reordering of tabs
* Ability to split a tab panel in half to have two tabs open side by side

See index.html for a demo an instructions.

http://jagthedrummer.github.io/fancy-tabs/
